	<h1>segway movie: part 1</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>We&#8217;ve been working on a movie featuring the Segway. I&#8217;ve put up <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20021225203857/http://www.aaronsw.com/movies/segway-part1.mov">Part 1 of the movie</a> (via the Internet Archive).</p>

<p>Like <a href="http://www.aaronsw.com/movies/">the rest of my movies</a> it&#8217;s more than a bit silly, but hopefully you&#8217;ll enjoy it. I&#8217;d enjoy hearing what you think.</p>

